  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a libvpx</title>

    <para>
      This package, from the WebM project, provides the reference implementations
of the VP8 Codec, used in most current html5 video, and of the
next-generation VP9 Codec.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

